 The country has a great variety of plant communities due to the diversity of its microclimates, soils and altitudes.
 The region is also home to a wide variety of animal and bird species.
 Rare animals such as the European brown bear, wolf, eagle, owl, lynx, wildcat and capercaillie can be seen here, as well as many other common species.
